title: The Superiority Of The King James Bible - Danny Jack
description:
This book has been written from the view point of the average person who wants to gain an understanding of how we got our English Bible and the differences in Bible versions. It is the writer's belief that there are many books out there written with the scholar in mind. This book was written so that anyone would be able to pick it up and gain a good understanding of the subject.


About the author:
Danny Jack Pastor of GUIDING LIGHT BAPTIST CHURCH Shag Harbour, Nova Scotia, Canada
